  "description": "<i>My Secret Diary</i> is a password protected journal game for the NDS. It features a diary, contacts book, calendar and mini games. The mini games include a word search, hangman style game and fortune telling. There is also the option to compare your friends compatibility with each other. <br><br>The game is part of the My Games series and features the My Games chat feature that enables players to connect with <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/my-make-up\">My Make-Up</a> and <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/my-dress-up\">My Dress-Up</a> for chat sessions. <br><br>The game has 9 languages: English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Finnish, Norwegian, Swedish and Danish.\n",
